<p>Physical constants are provided with their correct dimensions, enabling type-safe physics
calculations.</p>

<h3>Fundamental Constants</h3>

<pre><code class="language-lean">open Measures.Constants
open Measures.Units.SI

-- Speed of light
c  -- 299,792,458 m/s (exact)

-- Planck constant
h  -- 6.626e-34 J·s
ℏ  -- h / (2π), reduced Planck constant

-- Gravitational constant
G  -- 6.674e-11 m³/(kg·s²)</code></pre>

<h3>Mass-Energy Equivalence</h3>

<pre><code class="language-lean">-- E = mc²
def restMass := 1.0 *: kilogram
def energy := restMass *. c *. c

#eval energy.asUnit joule  -- ~8.99e16 J</code></pre>

